   000116                01  WS-PLACED-OVF        PIC 9(4) VALUE 0.                               |                                  
   000117                01  WS-HARD-FAIL         PIC 9(4) VALUE 0.                               |                                  
   000118                01  WS-MAX-OCC           PIC 9(2) VALUE 0.                               |                                  
   000119                01  WS-ROW-COUNT         PIC 9(8) VALUE 0.                               |                                  
   000120                01  WS-DEC-COUNT         PIC 9(8) VALUE 0.                               |                                  
   000121                01  WS-MISMATCH          PIC 9(8) VALUE 0.                               |                                  
   000122                01  WS-SAMPLE            PIC 9(2) VALUE 0.                               |                                  
