   000141                PROCEDURE DIVISION.                                                      |                                  
   000142                                                                                         |                                  
   000143                0000-MAIN SECTION.                                                       |                                  
   000144                    PERFORM 1000-GEN-COLUMN                                              |153                               
   000145                    PERFORM 2000-ENCODE                                                  |181                               
   000146                    PERFORM 3000-DECODE-VERIFY                                           |285                               
   000147                    PERFORM 9000-REPORT                                                  |317                               
   000148                    STOP RUN.                                                            |                                  
   000149                                                                                         |                                  
   000150               ******************************************************************        |                                  
   000151               *  1000 -- generate a low-cardinality string column                       |                                  
   000152               ******************************************************************        |                                  
   000153                1000-GEN-COLUMN SECTION.                                                 |                                  
   000154                1000-GEN.                                                                |                                  
   000155               *    build the vocabulary of N-DISTINCT distinct values                   |                                  
   000156                    PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-I > N-DISTINCT             |96 96 58                          
   000157      1                 MOVE WS-I TO WS-VZ                                               |96 110                            
   000158      1                 MOVE SPACES TO VOCAB(WS-I)                                       |IMP 96 85                         
   000159      1                 STRING 'CATEGORY-' DELIMITED BY SIZE                             |                                  
   000160      1                        WS-VZ       DELIMITED BY SIZE                             |110                               
   000161      1                     INTO VOCAB(WS-I)                                             |96 85                             
   000162                    END-PERFORM                                                          |                                  
   000163                                                                                         |                                  
   000164               *    write N-ROWS, each picking a vocabulary entry. A multiplier          |                                  
   000165               *    coprime to N-DISTINCT (257) cycles through ALL distinct values       |                                  
   000166               *    (so the dictionary really fills), scrambled rather than 1,2,3.       |                                  
   000167               *    Uniform repetition is the conservative case; real columns are        |                                  
   000168               *    skewed (Zipf), which only compresses better.                         |                                  
   000169                    OPEN OUTPUT COLUMN-FILE                                              |44                                
   000170                    PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-I > N-ROWS                 |96 96 59                          
   000171      1                 COMPUTE WS-T = WS-I * 257                                        |104 96                            
1PP 5737-L11 IBM COBOL for Linux                     1.2.0      DICTENC   Date 06/13/2026  Time 20:07:55   Page     5               
   LineID  PL SL  ----+-*A-1-B--+----2----+----3----+----4----+----5----+----6----+----7-|--+----8 Map and Cross Reference           
0  000172      1                 COMPUTE WS-VIDX = FUNCTION MOD(WS-T, N-DISTINCT) + 1             |111 IFN 104 58                    
   000173      1                 MOVE VOCAB(WS-VIDX) TO COL-STR                                   |111 85 46                         
   000174      1                 WRITE COL-REC                                                    |45                                
   000175                    END-PERFORM                                                          |                                  
   000176                    CLOSE COLUMN-FILE.                                                   |44                                
   000177                                                                                         |                                  
   000178               ******************************************************************        |                                  
   000179               *  2000 -- encode COLUMN.DAT through the tiny-pointer dictionary          |                                  
   000180               ******************************************************************        |                                  
   000181                2000-ENCODE SECTION.                                                     |                                  
   000182                2000-ENC.                                                                |                                  
   000183                    PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-I > NBKT                   |96 96 55                          
   000184      1                 MOVE 0 TO B-OCC(WS-I)                                            |96 70                             
   000185      1                 PERFORM VARYING WS-J FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-J > BSLOTS             |97 97 56                          
   000186      2                     MOVE 'N' TO DS-USED(WS-I, WS-J)                              |96 97 66                          
   000187      1                 END-PERFORM                                                      |                                  
   000188                    END-PERFORM                                                          |                                  
   000189                    PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-I > OVF-CAP                |96 96 57                          
   000190      1                 MOVE 'N' TO O-USED(WS-I)                                         |96 75                             
   000191                    END-PERFORM                                                          |                                  
   000192                    MOVE 0 TO WS-NEXT-CODE                                               |112                               
   000193                                                                                         |                                  
   000194                    OPEN INPUT COLUMN-FILE                                               |44                                
   000195                    OPEN OUTPUT ENCODED-FILE                                             |48                                
   000196                    MOVE 'N' TO WS-EOF                                                   |94                                
   000197                    PERFORM UNTIL EOF-YES                                                |95                                
   000198      1                 READ COLUMN-FILE                                                 |44                                
   000199      2                     AT END SET EOF-YES TO TRUE                                   |95                                
   000200      1                     NOT AT END                                                   |                                  
   000201      2                         ADD 1 TO WS-ROW-COUNT                                    |119                               
   000202      2                         MOVE COL-STR TO WS-HSTR                                  |46 106                            
   000203      2                         PERFORM 2100-DICT-ENCODE                                 |212                               
   000204      2                         MOVE WS-CODE TO EN-CODE                                  |107 50                            
   000205      2                         WRITE ENC-REC                                            |49                                
   000206      1                 END-READ                                                         |                                  
   000207                    END-PERFORM                                                          |                                  
   000208                    CLOSE COLUMN-FILE                                                    |44                                
   000209                    CLOSE ENCODED-FILE.                                                  |48                                
   000210                                                                                         |                                  
   000211               *    look the string up; if new, assign the next sequential code          |                                  
   000212                2100-DICT-ENCODE.                                                        |                                  
   000213                    PERFORM 2300-HASH                                                    |272                               
   000214                    MOVE 'N' TO WS-FOUND                                                 |108                               
   000215                    PERFORM VARYING WS-J FROM 1 BY 1                                     |97                                
   000216                            UNTIL WS-J > BSLOTS OR FOUND-YES                             |97 56 109                         
   000217      1                 IF DS-USED(WS-BKT, WS-J) = 'N'                                   |100 97 66                         
   000218      2                     MOVE 'Y'     TO DS-USED(WS-BKT, WS-J)                        |100 97 66                         
   000219      2                     MOVE WS-HSTR TO DS-STR(WS-BKT, WS-J)                         |106 100 97 67                     
   000220      2                     ADD 1 TO WS-NEXT-CODE                                        |112                               
   000221      2                     MOVE WS-NEXT-CODE TO DS-CODE(WS-BKT, WS-J)                   |112 100 97 68                     
   000222      2                     MOVE WS-HSTR TO CT-STR(WS-NEXT-CODE)                         |106 112 81                        
   000223      2                     MOVE WS-NEXT-CODE TO WS-CODE                                 |112 107                           
   000224      2                     ADD 1 TO B-OCC(WS-BKT)                                       |100 70                            
   000225      2                     ADD 1 TO WS-PLACED-BUCKET                                    |115                               
   000226      2                     SET FOUND-YES TO TRUE                                        |109                               
   000227      1                 ELSE                                                             |                                  
   000228      2                     IF DS-STR(WS-BKT, WS-J) = WS-HSTR                            |100 97 67 106                     
1PP 5737-L11 IBM COBOL for Linux                     1.2.0      DICTENC   Date 06/13/2026  Time 20:07:55   Page     6               
   LineID  PL SL  ----+-*A-1-B--+----2----+----3----+----4----+----5----+----6----+----7-|--+----8 Map and Cross Reference           
0  000229      3                         MOVE DS-CODE(WS-BKT, WS-J) TO WS-CODE                    |100 97 68 107                     
   000230      3                         SET FOUND-YES TO TRUE                                    |109                               
   000231      2                     END-IF                                                       |                                  
   000232      1                 END-IF                                                           |                                  
   000233                    END-PERFORM                                                          |                                  
   000234                    IF B-OCC(WS-BKT) > WS-MAX-OCC                                        |100 70 118                        
   000235      1                 MOVE B-OCC(WS-BKT) TO WS-MAX-OCC                                 |100 70 118                        
   000236                    END-IF                                                               |                                  
   000237                    IF NOT FOUND-YES                                                     |109                               
   000238      1                 PERFORM 2200-DICT-ENCODE-OVF                                     |242                               
   000239                    END-IF.                                                              |                                  
   000240                                                                                         |                                  
   000241               *    backup table : linear probe from a second hash of the key            |                                  
   000242                2200-DICT-ENCODE-OVF.                                                    |                                  
   000243                    COMPUTE WS-T  = WS-HV * 40503                                        |104 103                           
   000244                    COMPUTE WS-OH = FUNCTION MOD(WS-T, OVF-CAP)                          |101 IFN 104 57                    
   000245                    MOVE 'N' TO WS-FOUND                                                 |108                               
   000246                    PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 0 BY 1                                     |96                                
   000247                            UNTIL WS-I >= OVF-CAP OR FOUND-YES                           |96 57 109                         
   000248      1                 COMPUTE WS-STMP = WS-OH + WS-I                                   |102 101 96                        
   000249      1                 COMPUTE WS-S = FUNCTION MOD(WS-STMP, OVF-CAP) + 1                |99 IFN 102 57                     
   000250      1                 IF O-USED(WS-S) = 'N'                                            |99 75                             
   000251      2                     MOVE 'Y'     TO O-USED(WS-S)                                 |99 75                             
   000252      2                     MOVE WS-HSTR TO O-STR(WS-S)                                  |106 99 76                         
   000253      2                     ADD 1 TO WS-NEXT-CODE                                        |112                               
   000254      2                     MOVE WS-NEXT-CODE TO O-CODE(WS-S)                            |112 99 77                         
   000255      2                     MOVE WS-HSTR TO CT-STR(WS-NEXT-CODE)                         |106 112 81                        
   000256      2                     MOVE WS-NEXT-CODE TO WS-CODE                                 |112 107                           
   000257      2                     ADD 1 TO WS-PLACED-OVF                                       |116                               
   000258      2                     SET FOUND-YES TO TRUE                                        |109                               
   000259      1                 ELSE                                                             |                                  
   000260      2                     IF O-STR(WS-S) = WS-HSTR                                     |99 76 106                         
   000261      3                         MOVE O-CODE(WS-S) TO WS-CODE                             |99 77 107                         
   000262      3                         SET FOUND-YES TO TRUE                                    |109                               
   000263      2                     END-IF                                                       |                                  
   000264      1                 END-IF                                                           |                                  
   000265                    END-PERFORM                                                          |                                  
   000266                    IF NOT FOUND-YES                                                     |109                               
   000267      1                 ADD 1 TO WS-HARD-FAIL                                            |117                               
   000268      1                 MOVE 0 TO WS-CODE                                                |107                               
   000269                    END-IF.                                                              |                                  
   000270                                                                                         |                                  
   000271               *    rolling hash of WS-HSTR : H = H*31 + ord(ch) mod prime               |                                  
   000272                2300-HASH.                                                               |                                  
   000273                    MOVE 0 TO WS-HV                                                      |103                               
   000274                    PERFORM VARYING WS-K FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-K > STR-BYTES              |98 98 60                          
   000275      1                 COMPUTE WS-ORDV = FUNCTION ORD(WS-HSTR(WS-K:1))                  |105 IFN 98 106                    
   000276      1                 COMPUTE WS-T = WS-HV * 31                                        |104 103                           
   000277      1                 ADD WS-ORDV TO WS-T                                              |105 104                           
   000278      1                 COMPUTE WS-HV = FUNCTION MOD(WS-T, 2147483647)                   |103 IFN 104                       
   000279                    END-PERFORM                                                          |                                  
   000280                    COMPUTE WS-BKT = FUNCTION MOD(WS-HV, NBKT) + 1.                      |100 IFN 103 55                    
   000281                                                                                         |                                  
